2. **Fix #4.1** — Replace per-symbol Redis lookups with in-memory set checks
3. **Fix #6.2** — Sliding window SMA (saves ~50% computation)

### High Impact (2–4 hours each)
4. **Fix #5.2** — Incremental indicator updates instead of full recalc
5. **Fix #2.2** — Add Redis kline caching with interval-based TTLs
6. **Fix #3.1** — Add receive timeout for Binance WS zombie detection
7. **Fix #3.3** — Switch from `!ticker@arr` to per-symbol `@ticker` streams

### Longer Term
8. **Fix #2.1** — Shared Redis connection pool
9. **Fix #5.3** — Separate polling logic for stocks vs. crypto
10. **Fix #1.3** — Add retry/backoff across all external API calls
